for most of
the day, and triggered an
all-out manhunt.

01:21.815 --> 01:31.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Thick smoke and screams of panic
captured
by a cell phone moments after
double explosions

01:31.391 --> 01:38.198 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
