airport. Suitcases
stood abandoned as would-be
passengers scrambled

01:38.231 --> 01:40.867 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
over collapsed ceilings and
shattered windows.

01:40.901 --> 01:46.640 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: I hear an explosion. And
all the ceilings
is going down. And then I just
go under the

01:46.673 --> 01:51.578 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
