people with
blood.

01:55.048 --> 02:00.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): I
tried to flee
towards the arrivals and we
couldn't get there,

02:00.554 --> 02:06.326 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
