crash, crash,
crash everywhere. And we went
toward the taxis.

02:06.360 --> 02:09.463 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It was a total confusion. It was
truly hell.

02:09.496 --> 02:14.868 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Belgian prosecutors
say it was
the work of two suicide bombers,
attacking

02:14.901 --> 02:21.842 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
