have ever

02:53.940 --> 02:55.709 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
seen in my career.

02:55.742 --> 02:59.379 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The twin attacks,
