03:15.662 --> 03:17.464 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES MICHEL, Belgian Prime
Minister (through
translator): Ladies and
gentlemen, what we

03:17.497 --> 03:22.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
