leaders makes it very difficult
to sustain

33:17.696 --> 33:22.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
progress. So, even if somebody
puts something
in place, what often happens is
that it's

33:22.067 --> 33:26.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
