33:28.506 --> 33:32.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
APRIL BROWN: As new data comes
in, it's being
used to find out how well their
reforms are

33:32.510 --> 33:36.414 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
working. And Marc Cherna knows
his work is
far from finished.

33:36.448 --> 33:40.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARC CHERNA: I have been doing
this work for
over 40 years and if there was a
magic bullet,

33:40.719 --> 33:46.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
we wouldn't be talking about it
today. This
is very complex work. There is
no easy solution.

33:46.091 --> 33:49.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There have been billions and
billions of dollars
spent on this.

33:49.094 --> 33:53.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's a lot of people way
smarter than me
