still struggle

33:53.899 --> 33:55.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
with it.

33:55.333 --> 33:58.436 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
APRIL BROWN: For the "PBS
NewsHour," I'm April
Brown in Pittsburgh.

33:58.470 --> 34:03.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Online, you can read
more on how
data is being used to support
Pennsylvania's

34:03.909 --> 34:09.414 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
most vulnerable children.

34:09.447 --> 34:22.661 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The United
Nations Refugee
Agency says it will not
cooperate with a European

34:22.694 --> 34:26.965 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
