aimed at halting
the migrant flow. And the walls
being rebuilt

34:45.517 --> 34:50.588 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in Europe will likely only grow
taller after
today's attacks in Brussels.

34:50.622 --> 34:55.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
From the island of Lesbos, in
Greece, special
correspondent Malcolm Brabant
reports.

34:55.360 --> 34:59.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: This was one of
the last
boats to land on the beaches of
southern Lesbos.

34:59.998 --> 35:04.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was a desperate attempt to
beat the deadline
set by Europe, which effectively
shut down

35:04.836 --> 35:09.140 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the refugee trail.

35:09.174 --> 35:17.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The screams marked the moment of
realization
that two people had been
suffocated in the

35:17.649 --> 35:27.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
chaos and darkness of the
crossing. As medical
teams fought in vain to revive
the crush victims,

35:27.492 --> 35:31.229 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a Syrian called Bashir spoke to
the migrants'
aspirations.

35:31.262 --> 35:37.869 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: We hope they don't take
this into effect.
We hope that we can make it to
Europe. I don't

35:37.902 --> 35:43.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
