lucky, we
can move on. If we are not, I
don't know what

35:43.608 --> 35:45.377 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
will happen to us.

35:45.410 --> 35:48.546 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MALCOLM BRABANT: For two
consecutive nights,
the vigil of these volunteers on
the beaches

35:48.580 --> 35:55.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
