the moment,
been made redundant by the ships
of Frontex,

36:09.100 --> 36:13.204 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Europe's border agency,
patrolling the waters
dividing Turkey from Greece.

36:13.238 --> 36:18.977 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Yet volunteer Rebecca
Michaelides believes
the exodus from Turkey is just
temporarily

36:19.010 --> 36:20.879 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on hold.

36:20.912 --> 36:22.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REBECCA MICHAELIDES, Volunteer:
The people
will keep on coming because
they're very desperate

36:22.814 --> 36:30.922 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in leaving Turkey and just
trying for a better
future. Being turned back for us
and for myself

36:30.955 --> 36:34.426 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
