problem.

36:34.459 --> 36:40.465 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's a lot deeper, and going
back to as deep
as the war in Syria that needs
to be stopped,

36:40.498 --> 36:44.669 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but also to the hardship of
these people and
what they're going through, that
we need,

36:44.702 --> 36:46.905 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
as Europe, to be -- to help
them.

36:46.938 --> 36:52.210 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: The efforts to
reinforce
fortress Europe alarm Ahmad Ali,
a dentist

36:52.243 --> 36:57.348 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
from a besieged Syrian city
