relatives still in
Syria.

37:00.085 --> 37:07.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AHMAD ALI, Refugee: We don't
need to go back.
Everybody here is worried about
the situation,

37:07.792 --> 37:16.634 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
so we just -- we need to cross
the border
to search for our lives. We
can't stay here

37:16.668 --> 37:18.470 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for a long time.

37:18.503 --> 37:21.639 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Prime
candidates to be among
the first deported are
Pakistanis, who are

37:21.673 --> 37:28.179 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
