detention center

37:28.213 --> 37:33.451 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Lesbos to be registered. But
in a possible
blow to the E.U.-Turkey deal,
the United Nations

37:33.485 --> 37:38.523 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Refugee Agency said it wouldn't
