Islam.

38:01.446 --> 38:10.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IMRAN SHARIF, Refugee: If the
Greece government
puts me back in Pakistan, where
there are

38:10.889 --> 38:18.496 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
